data.description: Incredible colonial in the Highlands!  This huge 5 bedroom, 3 1/2 bath has it all.  On the first floor, there is a large, updated eat in kitchen with island, formal dining room, family room, half bath and office.  Upstairs you'll find the primary bedroom and bathroom, along with 4 additional large bedrooms and another full bathroom.  From the upstairs, the laundry chute leads to the first floor laundry room!  In the basement there is a large theater/family room, another full bathroom, and some storage area.  Outside is where you'll be the envy of your friends!  The gazebo has three TV's that make watching the big game(s) the best.  A three and a half car garage on the side compliment the home.  Schedule your personal showing today!!
